data.description: What a great opportunity.  This charming single story home has a great floor plan complete with 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, a kitchen with pull up seating that is open to the dining area, a living room that overlooks the back yard and a patio enclosure.  If you like the outdoors you are sure to love the back yard which is very spacious and has 3 sheds for storage and a covered patio.  There is even a 2 car attached garage with direct access to the rear.   This wonderful property is ready for you to call it home!  Come check it out for yourself before it's too late!  This is a HUD home and is Sold As-Is.
